# 詞: 睇怕

1. 佢好睇怕，所以一見到新同事就唔好說話。 (He is very afraid of new colleagues, so he doesn't speak to them.)
2. 我睇怕自己會搞砸，所以先唔好出嚟。 (I'm afraid I might mess up, so I'm not coming out yet.)
3. 佢好睇怕，所以每次去餐廳都帶人。 (He is very afraid, so he always brings someone when going to a restaurant.)
4. 我睇怕自己講唔到，所以先唔好問問題。 (I'm afraid I can't speak, so I'm not asking questions yet.)
5. 佢好睇怕，所以一見到陌生人都會躲開。 (He is very afraid, so he runs away from strangers.)
6. 我睇怕自己會犯錯，所以先唔好做決定。 (I'm afraid I might make a mistake, so I'm not making decisions yet.)
7. 佢好睇怕，所以一見到新環境就覺得好緊張。 (He is very afraid, so he feels very nervous when seeing a new environment.)
8. 我睇怕自己會搞砸，所以先唔好嘗試。 (I'm afraid I might mess up, so I'm not trying yet.)
9. 佢好睇怕，所以一見到陌生人就覺得好害怕。 (He is very afraid, so he feels very scared when seeing strangers.)
10. 我睇怕自己會搞砸，所以先唔好說話。 (I'm afraid I might mess up, so I'm not speaking yet.) [end of text]


